data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Insurance company does not require flood insurance from sellers. Welcome to this exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence located in the sought-after Rivercrest community in Riverview, FL. Boasting a contemporary open floor plan with tile throughout, this home offers a seamless blend of style and comfort. ** NEW Roof will be installed before closing with full price offer** The renovated kitchen is a highlight, providing a modern and functional space. Spectacular views of the pond and conservation area enhance the overall ambiance, creating a serene backdrop for daily living. The backyard is perfect for entertaining, providing a private space to relax and unwind. This home offers a unique opportunity to experience the best of the Rivercrest community while enjoying the comforts of a well-maintained and thoughtfully designed living space. Don't miss the chance to make this property your next home.       Enjoy the convenience of a split floor plan, providing privacy and flexibility for various living arrangements. With an easy commute to Tampa and MacDill Air Force Base, this residence is strategically positioned for those seeking accessibility. Beyond the home's features, the Rivercrest community offers a host of amenities, including playgrounds, pools, a clubhouse, tennis courts, basketball courts, and more. Additionally, the property is in close proximity MacDill Airfare base, shopping centers and a variety of excellent dining options.
